<h2>_("Welcome to Blue Fruit!")</h2>
<p>Blue Fruit is a site to submit and view new releases of IWBTG fangames, a niche subgenre of freeware games. For more information visit the <a href="/about">About</a> page.</p>
<p>English and Japanese translations are availble in the top right corner.</p>
<h3>_("New Releases")</h3>
<div class="releases">
{{~it.releases :group:index}}
  {{=group.date}}
  {{~group.games :game:index2}}
    <br/>
    <a href="{{=game.link}}">{{=game.name}}</a> - {{=game.authors}}
  {{~}}
  <br/>
{{~}}
</div>

<h3>_("Updates")</h3>
<div class="releases">
{{~it.updates :group:index}}
  {{=group.date}}
  {{~group.games :game:index2}}
    <br/>
    <a href="{{=game.link}}">{{=game.name}}</a> - {{=game.authors}}
  {{~}}
  <br/>
{{~}}
</div>
